OL,3,CFears meals on wheels could be axed
OL,4,Camid council cuts
OL,6,FThere are calls for a Welsh council
OL,7,Fnot to axe its meals-on-wheels service
OL,8,Fin an attempt to save money.
OL,10,FCaerphilly Council announced proposals
OL,11,Flast month to cut the Meals Direct
OL,12,Fservice by November this year and
OL,13,Freplace it with an external provider.
OL,15,FIt comes as the council has also
OL,16,Fproposed cutting funding for popular
OL,17,Ftourist attractions and cultural
OL,18,Fvenues in the borough ` such as
OL,19,FLlancaiach Fawr Manor and the
OL,20,FBlackwood Miners' Institute ` in order
OL,21,Fto balance its books.
