OL,6,FThe council has said it must deliver
OL,7,Fsavings in the region of #45million
OL,8,Fover the next two years to survive.
OL,10,FThe meals-on-wheels service currently
OL,11,Fcosts #444,000 to run.
OL,13,FThe service delivers around 125,000
OL,14,Fmeals a year to around 320 people in
OL,15,Fthe borough supported by a workforce
OL,16,Fof more than 30 caterers, drivers and
OL,17,Fhelpers.
OL,19,FPeople get meals delivered to their
OL,20,Fhomes for a payment of between #5 and
OL,21,F#6 a day.
