OL,6,FRetired nurse Margaret, who began her
OL,7,Fcareer in the 1950s at a tuberculosis
OL,8,Fhospital in Gelligaer, has had the
OL,9,Fmeals delivered since she left
OL,10,Fhospital last year and pays #5 a day
OL,11,Ffor a hot lunch and a small dessert as
OL,12,Fwell as a prepared sandwich in the
OL,13,Fevening. Subsidised customers like
OL,14,FMargaret are assessed as in great need
OL,15,Fby social services. Non-subsidised
OL,16,Fusers pay around #6 a day.
