OL,6,FMargaret said: "I am housebound and
OL,7,FI'm not supposed to go out to mix. I'm
OL,8,F87, I'm not young anymore, and I can't
OL,9,Feven walk with a stick. I would be
OL,10,Fcompletely lost without it (the meals).
OL,12,F"When I first came out from the
OL,13,Fhospital I was burning everything
OL,14,Fbecause I was forgetting. It became
OL,15,Fdangerous. There is no way I can stand
OL,16,Fup for long enough safely enough to
OL,17,Fprepare anything for myself.
