OL,6,F"I've worked all of my life and paid
OL,7,Fall my taxes and I do feel it's now
OL,8,Ftime to be looked after a little bit,
OL,9,Fis it not? I worked six days out of
OL,10,Fseven in the hospitals and I worked 48
OL,11,Fhours a week. I enjoyed it, mind, I
OL,12,Fliked the work - but it was nothing
OL,13,Flike it is today.
OL,15,F"I see them with all their fancy
OL,16,Fclothes in the government on the
OL,17,Ftelevision. It's nice to see them
OL,18,Fdressed tidy, but I can't afford what
OL,19,Fthey can."
