OL,6,FNorman said: "I would really miss the
OL,7,Fdinners. It's been a great help to us
OL,8,Fto have that there. They were so good
OL,9,Fto me in the hospital in getting me on
OL,10,Fto these dinners and it'd be a
OL,11,Ftravesty to lose them. If I was living
OL,12,Fon my own without my wife it'd be even
OL,13,Fmore crucial. I can't imagine what
OL,14,Fit'd be like being alone and facing
OL,15,Flosing that."
