OL,3,CFears meals on wheels could be axed
OL,4,Camid council cuts
OL,6,FLianne Dallimore, Unison's Caerphilly
OL,7,FCounty branch secretary, said:
OL,8,F"Hundreds of elderly people, including
OL,9,Fsome who are blind and bed-bound, will
OL,10,Fbe devastated if the local authority
OL,11,Fends its Meals Direct service.
OL,13,F"This is an essential way to ensure
OL,14,Fthe most vulnerable people in the
OL,15,Fcommunity are nourished and have some
OL,16,Ffriendly contact.
OL,18,F"Ripping away this vital lifeline in
OL,19,Fthe name of cost savings is appalling
OL,20,Fand completely unacceptable.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
