OL,3,CFears meals on wheels could be axed
OL,4,Camid council cuts
OL,6,F"The closure would also mean job
OL,7,Flosses for the workers who bring fresh
OL,8,Fmeals to the doors of older people who
OL,9,Fstruggle to prepare food for
OL,10,Fthemselves.
OL,12,F"Unison will fight for everyone who
OL,13,Frelies on this important service and
OL,14,Ffor all the staff who work to deliver
OL,15,Fit."
OL,17,FCouncil leader Sean Morgan said: "We
OL,18,Fcan't continue to run our services in
OL,19,Fthe way we always have. We need to
OL,20,Fexplore all options and consider ways
OL,21,Fof doing things differently.
